                    "company": "De Nederlandsche Bank",
                    "description": "I was responsible for preparing all DNB\u2019s initial policy positioning for the development of the Eurosystem interbank system Target2, which led to a number of changes in the way of cooperation in the Eurosystem. I learned how the central bank payment system works, as well as the interbank market, and I further developed my skills of high-level communication on strategic and tactical topics relevant for DNB's board and the ECB. I actively participated in several international groups on payments systems and policy.",
